{
    "statusMessage": {
        "type": "text", /* text */
        "content": "Hi, how are you today?", /* text or url */
        "backgroundColor": "#008000", /* Optional for text only. Accepts any color code. Examples:
                                         #FFFFFF = White
                                         #0000FF = Blue
                                         #008000 = Green
                                         #FFFF00 = Yellow
                                         #FF0000 = Red
                                         #800080 = Purple
                                         #808080 = Gray
                                         #FFC0CB = Pink */
        "font": 1, /* Optional for text only. Accept the options below:
                      1 = SERIF
                      2 = NORICAN_REGULAR
                      3 = BRYNDAN_WRITE
                      4 = BEBASNEUE_REGULAR
                      5 = OSWALD_HEAVY */
        "allContacts": false, /* true to send to all contacts or
                               false to send to statusJidList below */ 
        "statusJidList": [
            "{{remoteJid}}@s.whatsapp.net"
        ]
    }
}
